title: Ep. - 313 - BABY GOD ON HBO ASSASSINS DIRECTOR RYAN WHITE
description:
Eve Wiley helps Kate review Baby God on HBO, which presents a haunting probe into the work of infamous Nevada fertility specialist Dr. Quincy Fortier, a man who deceived countless women struggling to conceive by using his own sperm — without their knowledge or consent — to impregnate them. ‌Eve is an activist working to bringing awareness and legislation to fertility frauds. In 2018 she found out her biological father was her mother’s fertility doctor.

 

Director Ryan White talks about his new documentary film Assassins, which examines the circumstances surrounding the murder of Kim Jong-nam, the half brother of North Korean leader Kim Jong-un.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
